2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes an end-to-end framework for learning attraction field maps. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the proposed framework involves learning from data. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and line segment detection, which are related to computer graphics. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as line segment detection is a common task in robotics for navigation and mapping.
